<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2465] system.bundle should be automatically wired to the relevant bundle</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2465</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When provisioning, it would be nice to automatically treat system.bundle as the system bundle symbolic name, so that users don&apos;t need to rely on the particular system bundle. For an example, in equinox, the system.bundle should be treated the same as the org.eclipse.osgi.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>n/a</environment>
        <key id="12468589">FELIX-2465</key>
            <summary>system.bundle should be automatically wired to the relevant bundle</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
